highlights.text: “Giữ Anh Cho Ngày Hôm Qua” by Hoàng Dũng, Rhymastic, and Lelarec is the highest new entry on Top Songs Vietnam at #77.
“Âm Thầm Bên Em” by Sơn Tùng M-TP has been on Top Songs Vietnam the longest, at 1664 days straight.
EM XINH "SAY HI" has the most spots on Top Songs Vietnam. “KHÔNG ĐAU NỮA RỒI” is the highest at #2.
“ANH VUI” by Phạm Kỳ is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Vietnam, up 48 spots at #108.
